<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="responsible-adj">responsible <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'spɒnsəbl/    美 /rɪ'spɑːnsəbl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>有责任的；尽责的；作为原由的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a responsible teacher 
负责的老师</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Human activity <strong>is</strong> not <strong>responsible for</strong> all water shortages. 
水资源短缺不完全是由人类活动造成的。</p><footer>2013 安徽</footer></div></div>